{"comments":"HoverEffect — Combined hover effect configuration.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nComposes all hover effect types into a single configuration:\n- Transform (scale, translate, rotate)\n- Style (brightness, shadows, filters)\n- Audio (enter/leave/loop sounds)\n- Animation (Lottie, CSS, spring)\n- Particle (sparkles, confetti, etc.)\n\n## Timing\n\nAll effects share common timing parameters:\n- `transitionDurationMs`: How long transitions take\n- `transitionDelay`: Delay before starting\n\n## Examples\n\n```purescript\n-- Basic hover with lift and shadow\nbasicHover = defaultHoverEffect\n\n-- Complex hover with audio and particles\nfancyHover = hoverEffect\n  { transform: liftTransform\n  , style: glowHoverStyle\n  , audio: hoverAudioEnter (HoverAudioUrl \"/click.mp3\") 0.5\n  , animation: noHoverAnimation\n  , particle: hoverParticleBurst SparkleParticle 10\n  , transitionDurationMs: 200.0\n  , transitionDelay: 0.0\n  }\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["transform",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Transform"],"HoverTransform"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["style",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Style"],"HoverStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["audio",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Audio"],"HoverAudio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["animation",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Animation"],"HoverAnimation"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["particle",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Particle"],"HoverParticle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["transitionDurationM